snippet.title: Bagman Comes Back (Bagman remake for Windows) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download Bagman Comes Back from https://lowcarb.itch.io

This game is a homage to Bagman, an arcade game released by Valadon Automation in 1982.

This version is made up of 8 completely new stages.

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com)

Read the "ReadMe.txt" file for more info.
